♪ I'll remember

02:03:11.980 --> 02:03:13.903
♪ I'll remember you

02:03:14.020 --> 02:03:15.943
♪ I'll remember you

02:03:16.060 --> 02:03:17.983
♪ Yes, I will

02:03:19.100 --> 02:03:21.023
♪ Help me out

02:03:22.500 --> 02:03:24.423
♪ Don't matter what happens

02:03:25.540 --> 02:03:27.668
♪ Time ain't gonna change nothing, baby

02:03:28.780 --> 02:03:32.102
♪ We could be halfway across the world
